rows.name:
Do you know Jo? She's one of my baristas,
and she's been acting a little strange lately.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021902_MSG0002
rows.name:
It's been that way ever since I put her in charge of our
brand-new espresso machine. Don't tell me she...
Oh, not AGAIN![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev021902_MSG0003
rows.name:
Look, I know she wouldn't say anything to me about it,
so can you talk to her instead? Figure out what's up,
and your next drink will be on the house![ST:wait ]
